text:
Hey Kamil, welcome in! I would suggest making a custom module that is changed via a choice field. Create a list of options in the module for potential senders then in the HTML/HubL editor set up some logic like this:

{% if module.sender == "Employee 1" %}
    &lt;HTML for Employee 1's signature /&gt;
{% elif module.sender == "Employee 2" %}
    &lt;HTML for Employee 2's signature /&gt;
... and so on for the rest of your options
{% endif %}

That way the email senders don't need to mess with any code when composing their emails :slightly_smiling_face: Let me know if any of that doesn't make sense!
